9-08-13T02:46:17.000Z","msg":"依家似乎開唔到新A/C，代任職機場多年既老友POST<br />\n希望入機場手足留意<br />\n<br />\n1.唔好大安旨意，以為尋日無事，黑警無清場，<br />\n今日、明日一樣無事。<br />\n尋日大家有經驗，幾千人要由機場走<br />\n係好困難既事<br />\n黑警要封場，手足走唔到，就會大量被捕<br />\n<br />\n2.機場有秘密通道，平時官員都係由此出閘<br />\n官方可以安排抵港旅客在此通關離開<br />\n所以大家見到仍有機來港，<br />\n都不一定代表會有旅客在T1/T2出閘<br />\n黑警可能安排佢地由密道走，再在大堂拉手足<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫大家唔好去，建議大家小心，勿輕敵。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nA8e343.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnA8e343.jpg&h=ba1ea0a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5803c9ab4d2c92bf644deec8d3702094f64066c4","tid":1460200,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:46:52.000Z","msg":"搵警察換黑衫搞事抹黑<br />\n<br />\n咁就出獅有名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n811夜晚鏡頭影到晒 全部有螢光棒做記認<br />\n<br />\n拎彈弓條女 鐵證如山"},{"pid":"b269acbb4a17d806ad883de204003dd5723338c5","tid":1460200,"uid":146118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2e122e33442f9d4f60b8b34e03835518bd957f","tid":1460200,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:48:00.000Z","msg":"我係前狗隊高級督察 狗隊部署你問我答<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460251</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n捉d落單嘅人 係黑社會老夾咁"},{"pid":"24fda9c4ef3cc3d399bcbfadba647fb533c8de49","tid":1460200,"uid":16372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:50:59.000Z","msg":"其他：老解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}